title: Issue concerning evaluate network issue and beyond

### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

So I re-trained the network from scratch and also through refine labels and I can't evaluate the network. I could create, analyze and label the videos before, but after re-training, I can't do anything past the "evaluate network" step. I have no idea where the issue is and I get a very long message, please see attached code.

### Operating System

operating system: windows 10

### DeepLabCut version

dlc version: I don't know. I get this message for both commands: 'import' is not recognized as an internal or external command, operable program or batch file.

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

gpu: NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2080 Ti

### Steps To Reproduce

_No response_
